* Dutch: [[vooringenomenheid]] (in its first meaning as predisposition),derived from the adjective [[vooringenomen]]/biased,predisposed
*German: [[Voreingenommenheit]] ''f'' (in its first meaning as predisposition),derived from the adjective [[Voreingenommen]]/biased,predisposed
*Portuguese: [[Polarização (em eletrônica)]]
*Norwegian: [[Fordom]]

